{"TopicId":103502,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"How to link within text?","CreatedByName":"Zucal","CreatedById":139764,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T05:59:16Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Zucal","CreatedById":139764,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T05:59:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIs there a way to embed links within text so that \u0022this\u0022 word could be a link? If so, teach me! Thanks.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Teoman2","CreatedById":113901,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T06:01:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/misc.php?do=bbcode\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/misc.php?do=bbcode\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou\u0027re welcome\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T06:59:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ETry it on my thread:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/113844-The-great-forum-test-thread%21\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/113844-The-great-forum-test-thread%21\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s how it works:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E[noparse]\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/113844-The-great-forum-test-thread%21\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/113844-The-great-forum-test-thread%21\u003C/a\u003E[/noparse]\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf you want to display a different text:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E[noparse]\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/113844-The-great-forum-test-thread%21\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EThe great forum test thread\u003C/a\u003E[/noparse]\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor images:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E[noparse]\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/113844-The-great-forum-test-thread%21\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/zWgULVG.png?1\u0022 alt=\u0022zWgULVG.png?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E[/noparse]\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-04-06T07:02:09Z\u0022 title=\u002204/06/2015 07:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EApril 6, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Mad Rocket Scientist\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T08:01:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Zucal\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Zucal\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIs there a way to embed links within text so that \u0022this\u0022 word could be a link? If so, teach me! Thanks.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo offence, but have you ever bothered to look what the little icons above the text field are for?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T12:01:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe easy way is to type the word you want linked, highlight it, then click the little icon of a globe with two links of chain on it. That will pop up a window to enter the link, which will be automatically applied to the highlighted text.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Zucal","CreatedById":139764,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-06T13:50:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks everyone for the solutions!\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}